Test Cases as Given

Sign up
--------------------
URL: https://bit.ly/2QjiQ6t

Directly leading to this page drop an error so the code is opening the front/main page and then navigating to the Sign up page


This page allows users to sign up to the cockpit application.
Expected behaviour or this page:
1. The “Vorname” field is required
2. The “Vorname” field must have at least 3 letters
3. The “Nachname” field is required
4. The “Nachname” field must have at least 3 letters
5. The “Email” field is required
6. The “Email” value should be a valid email
7. The “Email” is unique, so if there’s an email already registered, the email should be invalid
8. The “Passwort” field is required
9. Checking the “Ich akzeptiere die AGB und nehme die Datenschutzerklärung zur
Kenntnis.” checkbox is required.
10. The “Button” is inactive if the form fields are invalid
11. The “Button” is active when the form fields are valid
12. When are the fields are valid and the users clicks on “Registrieren”, it should go to the
“Welcome to Pylot” page


Sign in
--------------------------
URL: https://bit.ly/37qzerE

Directly leading to this page drop an error so the code is opening the front/main page and then navigating to the Sign up page

This page allows existing users to sign in to the cockpit application.
Expected behaviour or this page:
1. When the value of the fields “Email” and “Password” match to an existing user, the user
should be successful logged in
2. When the value of the fields “Email” and “Password” don’t match to an existing user, the
user should see the “Die Anmeldung ist fehlgeschlagen. Das Password und die email
stimmen nicht überein. Bitte versuchen Sie es erneut.” error message

